Helpfile
ngram tool
USAGE: ./ngram [filename] [item number] [top ngrams] [keyword]

filename:
	Name of the file you wish to analyse.

item number:
	number of items that form an n-gram. Default is 3.

top ngrams:
	number of top most frequent n-grams to output, default is 10.

keyword:
	One of the keywords: word, char, decimal indicating whether the n-gram items are words, 
	characters, or decimal digits.
